download git
install git with programs is path
add your name and email address in git using following command
git config --global user.name "Your Name"
git config --global user.email example@email.com
git config --global color.ui auto

clone project from bitbucket
git clone address

show configuations
git config -l

to view status of file(s)
git status

to view status of file(s) in oneline
git status -s

to add a created file
git add filename

to add deleted file
git add -u filename

to commit a file to local repo
git commit -m "comment"

to add and commit a file together
git commit -a -m "comment"

to push the commit in remote
git push origin master

to pull the remote changes
git pull origin master

to view log (commit history)
git log

to view log in one line
git log --oneline

to revert back to previous commit with code changes removal
git checkout commithash

to revert back to previous commit with code
git reset --soft commithash

to view all branch
git branch

to create a branch
git branch branchname

to add a left commit to a branch
git branch branchname commithash

to remove a branch
git branch -d branchname

to remove branch remotely
git push origin --delete branchname

to merge a branch
git merge branchname

to push branch to remote
git push origin branchname
